702421f-a.title: Brooklyn: 5th Street (South) - Rodney Street
702421f-a.text:
South 5th Street, south side, at Rodney Street, view-
ing west and across the latter (truck) from near Keap St.
and showing a W. P. A. street improvement project. On
the left is St. Pauls Evangelical Lutheran Church.
September 25, 1935
Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE
